  "root_text": {
    "sn43.44:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 43.44 ",
    "sn43.44:0.2": "2. Dutiyavagga ",
    "sn43.44:0.3": "Parāyanasutta ",
    "sn43.44:1.1": "“Parāyanañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi parāyanagāmiñca maggaṁ. ",
    "sn43.44:1.2": "Taṁ suṇātha. ",
    "sn43.44:1.3": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, parāyanaṁ? ",
    "sn43.44:1.4": "Yo, bhikkhave, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—",
    "sn43.44:1.5": "idaṁ vuccati, bhikkhave, parāyanaṁ. ",
    "sn43.44:1.6": "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, parāyanagāmī maggo? ",
    "sn43.44:1.7": "Kāyagatāsati. ",
    "sn43.44:1.8": "Ayaṁ vuccati, bhikkhave, parāyanagāmimaggo. ",
    "sn43.44:1.9": "Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṁ vo mayā parāyanaṁ, desito parāyanagāmimaggo. ",
    "sn43.44:1.10": "Yaṁ, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṁ sāvakānaṁ hitesinā anukampakena anukampaṁ upādāya, kataṁ vo taṁ mayā. ",
    "sn43.44:1.11": "Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyatha, bhikkhave, mā pamādattha; mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha. Ayaṁ vo amhākaṁ anusāsanī”ti. ",
    "sn43.44:1.12": "(Yathā asaṅkhataṁ tathā vitthāretabbaṁ.) ",
    "sn43.44:1.13": "Tettiṁsatimaṁ. ",
    "sn43.44:1.14": "Dutiyo vaggo. ",
    "sn43.44:2.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "sn43.44:2.1": "Asaṅkhataṁ anataṁ anāsavaṁ, ",
    "sn43.44:2.2": "Saccañca pāraṁ nipuṇaṁ sududdasaṁ; ",
    "sn43.44:2.3": "Ajajjaraṁ dhuvaṁ apalokitaṁ, ",
    "sn43.44:2.4": "Anidassanaṁ nippapañca santaṁ. ",
    "sn43.44:3.1": "Amataṁ paṇītañca sivañca khemaṁ, ",
    "sn43.44:3.2": "Taṇhākkhayo acchariyañca abbhutaṁ; ",
    "sn43.44:3.3": "Anītikaṁ anītikadhammaṁ, ",
    "sn43.44:3.4": "Nibbānametaṁ sugatena desitaṁ. ",
    "sn43.44:4.1": "Abyābajjho virāgo ca, ",
    "sn43.44:4.2": "suddhi mutti anālayo; ",
    "sn43.44:4.3": "Dīpo leṇañca tāṇañca, ",
    "sn43.44:4.4": "saraṇañca parāyananti. ",
    "sn43.44:4.5": "Asaṅkhatasaṁyuttaṁ samattaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn43.44:0.1": "Linked Discourses 43.44 ",
    "sn43.44:0.2": "Chapter Two ",
    "sn43.44:0.3": "The Final Haven ",
    "sn43.44:1.1": "“Mendicants, I will teach you the final haven and the path that leads to the final haven. ",
    "sn43.44:1.2": "Listen … ",
    "sn43.44:1.3": "And what is the final haven? ",
    "sn43.44:1.4": "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. ",
    "sn43.44:1.5": "This is called the final haven. ",
    "sn43.44:1.6": "And what is the path that leads to the final haven? ",
    "sn43.44:1.7": "Mindfulness of the body. ",
    "sn43.44:1.8": "This is called the path that leads to the final haven. ",
    "sn43.44:1.9": "So, mendicants, I’ve taught you the final haven and the path that leads to the final haven. ",
    "sn43.44:1.10": "Out of sympathy, I’ve done what a teacher should do who wants what’s best for their disciples. ",
    "sn43.44:1.11": "Here are these roots of trees, and here are these empty huts. Practice absorption, mendicants! Don’t be negligent! Don’t regret it later! This is my instruction to you.” ",
    "sn43.44:1.12": "(Tell in full as in the unconditioned.) ",
